<collectionCode box="[376,444,1634,1660]" pageId="2" pageNumber="115">IUCN</collectionCode>
Red List status – 
<collectionCode box="[645,689,1635,1661]" country="India" lsid="urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:13033" name="Forest Research Institute, Indian Council of Forestry Research and Education" pageId="2" pageNumber="115" type="Herbarium">DD</collectionCode>
.
